title: Chris Wilson - King For A Day
description:
RELEASE DETAILS
Year of release: 2002
Lable: Forge
Catalogue Number: Forge 1
Producer: Kerryn Tolhurst
Engineer: Barry Stockley
Recorded: St. Andrews Studios and Fatsounds Studios, West Melbourne, Australia, May 2002

The Players:
Chris Wilson - Vocals, & Harmonica
Shannon Bourne - Electric & Acoustic Guitars

Dave Folley - Drums & Percussion

Skip Sail - Banjo on Jesus Took Possession
Sarah Carroll - Vocals on Embers Down The Mountain
Cindy Boste - Vocals on You Got It Right The First Time
